使用YUM下载 rpm包
yum install --downloadonly --downloaddir=/tmp <package-name> 

yum -y install --downloadonly --downloaddir=/opt/softs/docker docker-ce.x86_64

yum -y install --downloadonly --downloaddir=/tmp libcgroup

yum install -y yum-utils device-mapper-persistent-data lvm2


yum -y install --downloadonly --downloaddir=/tmp rubygems-1.3.7-5.el6.noarch.rpm

yum list | grep rubygems


在当前目录下载
yumdownloader ruby 

下载所有依赖包:
yumdownloader --resolve --destdir /tmp tenlent-server